 
<p>
The <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2022/jul/27/dreamworld-rollercoaster-was-built-with-27m-tagged-for-koala-research-government-says">Tyre Extinguishers campaign</a> against gas-guzzling SUVs by deflating
their tires, and leaving leaflets on the cars thus targeted.
<p>
Students at the University of Cambridge persuaded the university <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/2022/07/25/student-climate-campaigners-welcome-momentous-victory-cambridge">not
to name a research lab in honor of Billionaire Polluters</a>.
<p>
*Adopting a policy to reject "all fossil fuel
industry funding and research partnerships" is what's needed.*

 